text: is a female Japanese sportswoman. She is best known as an archer who competed in the Summer Olympic Games.SportsReference.com (SR/Olympics), "Kaori Kawanaka" ; retrieved 2012-8-3. ==Career== Kawanaka was part of a team which won the bronze medal in women's archery at the 2012 Summer Olympics.Mitsuhashi, Makoto. "Japan archers on target," Yomiuri Shimbun (Japan). July 31, 2012; retrieved 2012-8-3.
